Package: gtscales
Title: Color Scale Extensions for 'gt'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Christopher T.",
           family = "Kenny",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ctkenny@proton.me",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9386-6860"))
Description: Adds compact legend helpers for 'gt' tables so color-encoded
    columns can be explained inside the rendered table. The primary interface
    combines 'gt::data_color()' with matched legends for continuous, binned,
    and discrete scales, with lower-level helpers available for legend-only
    workflows.
